enchantment.ffenchants.bloodlust.desc: Gives the wielder strength when a mob is killed.
enchantment.ffenchants.vampiric.desc: Has a chance to heal the wielder on hit.
enchantment.ffenchants.weighted.desc: Critical hits have a chance to inflict weakness.
enchantment.ffenchants.searing.desc: Has a chance to light mobs that hit you on fire.
enchantment.ffenchants.steadfast.desc: Reduces knockback taken and knocks back attackers.
enchantment.ffenchants.outrush.desc: Deals increased damage to fire mobs.
enchantment.ffenchants.torrent.desc: Increases entities' swimming speed while the trident is being held.
enchantment.ffenchants.aquatic_rejuvenat: Regenerates the durability of tridents while being held in water or rain.
enchantment.ffenchants.obsidian_skull.de: Reduces damage taken when flying into walls with an elytra.
enchantment.ffenchants.buoyancy_horse.de: Allows horses to float in water while being ridden.
enchantment.ffenchants.quickness_horse.d: Increases the movement speed of horses.
enchantment.ffenchants.maelstrom.desc: Pulls in mobs towards the trident and damages them.
enchantment.ffenchants.inferno.desc: Sets mobs near arrows fired from a crossbow on fire.
enchantment.ffenchants.anchoring_curse.d: Causes the wearer to sink faster in water.
